Acc Impairment in Afrikaans: Ongeval Wanfunksie
FVOCI (IFRS9) word vertaal as \"Geskatte Reële Waarde met Veranderinge in Eie Vermoë (IFRS9)\" in Afrikaans.
Do you mean to translate the word \"subsidiaries\" into Afrikaans? If so, the translation would be \"filiale.\"
Acc Impair in Afrikaans would be \"Rekening Verminder\".
Acc Amort can be translated to \"Akkoord Amortisasie\" in Afrikaans.
Acc Dep can be translated into Afrikaans as \"Rek Dep\".
In Afrikaans, \"Owned\" can be translated as \"Besit\".
FVPL can be translated to Afrikaans as \"BVGW\" (Beskikbaar vir Verkoop teen Waarde).
CGT stands for \"Capital Gains Tax\" in Afrikaans.
IS2 can be translated into Afrikaans as \"IS2\".
IS3 kan vertaal word as \"IS3\" in Afrikaans.
IS5 can be translated into Afrikaans as \"IS5\" since it is an acronym or abbreviation that does not have a specific meaning in the Afrikaans language.
SDL stands for Simple DirectMedia Layer.
STC can be translated into Afrikaans as \"STC\". The abbreviation remains the same in both languages.
The translation of \"UIF\" into Afrikaans is \"WVF\" which stands for \"Werkloosheidsversekeringfonds\".
